title: Everton vs. Southampton - English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Everton lost their last home league match against Southampton in January 2023, ending a 17-game unbeaten run against Saints at Goodison Park. They last lost consecutive home league games against them in April 1974. Following their 1-0 win at St Mary’s in the reverse fixture, Southampton are looking to complete the league double over Everton for the first time since 1997-98.

title: Arsenal vs. Newcastle United - English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Arsenal have lost just one of their last 20 Premier League home games against Newcastle, winning 11 of the last 12 since a 1-0 loss in November 2010. Following their 1-0 win at St James’ Park in November, Newcastle are looking to complete their first league double over Arsenal since 1994-95.

title: Roland-Garros 2025- The Preview Show
description: As Roland-Garros 20 5 swings into view, we look ahead to 15 days of captivating competition. The ultimate prize in clay court tennis is once again up for grabs and soon Paris will welcome the world’s greatest players, some with it all to prove, others with a legacy to fight for. There will be players searching for a career-defining breakthrough, and those hoping to shock the tennis world. All of them desperate to write their own history, here, on the game’s greatest stage.

title: PSG ..Road to the UCL Final 2025
description: Paris Saint-Germain has qualified for the Champions League final for the second time after a performance that delighted its fans. The team achieved excellent results in this seasons European competition. Lets remember how the French champions arrived in Munich, where they are looking to claim their first title in the prestigious tournament.

title: Inter .. Road to the UCL Final 2025
description: Inter surprised many by qualifying for this seasons Champions League final despite facing strong teams in the knockout stages. The Italian team has previously won the European title three times. They reached the Munich final after intense matches, most notably two semifinal matches against Barcelona.

title: LaLiga BEST 11 - Luis García
description: Luis Garcia was a striker who played 8 seasons in La Liga. He played for Barcelona, Real Valladolid, Atletico Madrid and Real Racing in La Liga. In his career he played 473 games, scoring 115 goals.

title: La Liga World 2024/25 Ep.41
description: A program of interviews and reports I which all LALIGA clubs are represented The program lasts 26 minutes and every week presents all the latest personal stories and the more human-interest side of the competition in a slow-paced and polished format.

title: Osasuna vs Espanyol - LaLiga 2024/25 Week 37
description: Osasuna have not lost any of their last seven LaLiga games against Espanyol, equalling their best unbeaten run against them in the top-flight, achieved between 1987 and 1991. Espanyol have won just two of their last 10 LaLiga away games against Osasuna, with those the only games in which they have managed to score during this period - 2-0 in April 2013 and 2-1 in September 2016.

title: Atletico Madrid vs Real Betis - LaLiga 2024/25 Week 37
description: Atletico de Madrid have not lost any of their last 11 home games against Real Betis in LaLiga, winning the last six, the best run of consecutive home wins against the green-and-white side in their entire history in the competition. Following their 1-0 win at the Benito Villamarín in October 2024, Real Betis have the chance to win two games against Atletico de Madrid in the same LaLiga season for the fourth time in their history after 1986/87, 1994/95 and 2004/05.

title: LaLiga Power Ep.8
description: LALIGA Power is a program that pays tribute to all those who inspire the world through the values of football. In each episode, we discover the passion celebrities have for their club and experience a match day with the most dedicated fans in the world, as well as showing curiosities about LALIGA clubs and players. Because they are the strength of our football.

title: Mallorca vs Getafe - LaLiga 2024/25 Week 37
description: Mallorca have not lost any of their last four games against Getafe in LaLiga, equalling their best unbeaten run against them in the top-flight, achieved in their first four meetings between 2004 and 2006. Getafe have taken points in five of their last six LaLiga away games against Mallorca, this after having lost six of their first seven visits to the island in the competition.

title: Valencia vs Athletic Bilbao - LaLiga 2024/25 Week 37
description: Valencia have won just one of their last five home games against Athletic Club in LaLiga, winning 1-0 in their last meeting at Mestalla in January 2024, this after having won three in a row between February 2017 and March 2019 beforehand. Athletic Club have won three of their last five meetings with Valencia in LaLiga, this after having managed just one win in their previous 11 meetings in the competition beforehand.

title: Nantes vs Montpellier - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 34
description: Nantes have won 64.3% of their Ligue 1 home games against Montpellier in the 21st century, their highest success rate against an opponent they have faced 10+ times on home soil during this period. Since their return to the top-flight in 2013-14, Nantes have finished just two of their last 11 Ligue 1 campaigns with a victory : 1-0 v Strasbourg in 2017-18 and 1-0 v Angers in 2022-23.

title: In The Footsteps of Marquinhos - Ligue 1 Documentary 2024/25
description: From Brazil to France, beIN tells you the impressive journey of the Captain of Paris Saint-Germain. With 300 Ligue 1 matches recently played, discover the story of Marquinhos!

title: Olympique Marseille vs Rennes - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 34
description: Marseille have won three of their last four home games against Rennes in Ligue 1, each time without conceding a single goal. OM have kept 12 clean sheets at home against SRFC in the 21st century, at least two more than against any other team during this period. Marseille have finished just one of the last 12 Ligue 1 seasons with a defeat, losing 1-0 at Ajaccio on 3 June 2023.

title: Strasbourg vs Le Havre - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 34
description: The 39 meetings between Strasbourg and Le Havre in Ligue 1 have produced only three draws, a ratio of 7.7%. This is the lowest percentage of draws between two Ligue 1 teams among those who have faced each other 20+ times. Strasbourg have lost their last three matches to finish a Ligue 1 season, but they have been away from home each time, at Marseille, Lorient and Lyon in the last three years. At home, RCSA have gone three games to close a season without losing.

title: Nice vs Brest - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 34
description: Nice have lost only one of their last eight Ligue 1 games against Brest. The last five Nice-Brest matches in Ligue 1 have produced just three goals, or 0.6 per game, the lowest average among meetings played in each of the last three seasons. Nice have won five of their last six matches to finish a Ligue 1 season, sharing the points in their most recent one. The last defeat of OGCN to end a season in the top-flight dates to 2017-18.

title: Olympique Lyonnais vs Angers SCO - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 34
description: Lyon have won nine of their last ten matches against Angers in Ligue 1, scoring at least three goals in the last four. Lyon have won their final game in 15 of the last 24 Ligue 1 seasons in the 21st century, more than any other team. However, OL have ended two of the last four league campaigns with a defeat: both times against Nice.

title: PSG vs Auxerre - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 34
description: Paris SG have not lost any of their last five matches against Auxerre in Ligue 1. PSG are also unbeaten in their last 37 home games against a promoted side in Ligue 1 – scoring an average of 2.9 goals – since a defeat against Montpellier in their last match of the 2009-10 season. The last draw between Paris SG and Auxerre at the Parc des Princes in Ligue 1 was in December 2001. Since then, the 11 clashes between the two teams in the top-flight have seen eight wins for Paris and three for Auxerre.

title: Freiburg vs Eintracht Frankfurt - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 34
description: This fixture is SC Freiburg’s 850th Bundesliga match. They have only won one of their last 10 top-flight meetings with Eintracht Frankfurt and are winless in their last five, their longest ever wait for victory against the Eagles. SC Freiburg have picked up 13 of a possible 15 points over the last five matchdays, a joint league high together with Borussia Dortmund. Eintracht Frankfurt have also remained unbeaten during this period, conceding the joint-fewest goals in the league.

title: Heidenheim vs Werder Bremen - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 34
description: Werder Bremen and 1. FC Heidenheim have met three times in the Bundesliga and Werder are still yet to win. Of teams currently in the top flight, Heidenheim have only otherwise picked up points in every Bundesliga meeting with Union Berlin. 1. FC Heidenheim will finish no lower than 16th and are three points and six goals adrift of 15th place – since three points per win was introduced, only Borussia Monchengladbach in 1997/98 and VfB Stuttgart in 2021/22 have ever made up a three-point deficit to 15th on the final matchday.

title: Finals - ATP 250 Gonet Geneva Open - Switzerland 2025
description: The Gonet Geneva Open is a premier ATP 250 clay-court tournament held at the historic Tennis Club de Genève in Parc des Eaux-Vives. Celebrating its 10th anniversary in 2025, the event attracts top-tier talent as a key warm-up to Roland Garros. This years field features stars like Novak Djokovic, Taylor Fritz, and three-time champion Casper Ruud, promising a week of world-class tennis in a picturesque lakeside setting.

title: PSG vs Montpellier - Final French Cup Handball 2025
description: In a highly anticipated showdown at the Accor Arena in Paris, French handball giants Paris Saint-Germain and Montpellier clash in the 2025 Coupe de France final. With both teams showcasing exceptional form throughout the season, this match promises intense competition and thrilling moments as they vie for national glory.

title: Mixed Doubles - Day 6 Session 01 - ITTF World Table Tennis Championships Finals Doha 2025 Table 1

title: Lethal Weapon: Jesses Girl
description: After a break-in turns into a homicide, Murtaugh and Riggs set out to find the culprit. Murtaugh and Trish question their trust in Riana as she gets into trouble with friends. Meanwhile, Riggs recalls his troubling childhood and finds a true family with Molly and Ben.

title: Lethal Weapon: Family Ties
description: On Murtaughs first day on the job as interim captain, the wife of a popular businessman is abducted and the squad finds a connection in the case to Riggs father. Meanwhile, Riggs is left to grapple with his family and work.

title: Lethal Weapon: One Day More
description: The squads on high alert after a threat is made on Riggs life. With Murtaugh taking on more responsibility at work, he and Riggs have to deal with their changing relationship. Meanwhile, Trish gets caught up in some trouble and Molly asks Riggs to make a big decision.

title: Lethal Weapon: In The Same Boat
description: When Wesley Cole returns home and assumes duty as a LAPD police officer, the former international CIA operative finds himself navigating a new partnership with Murtaugh as he adjusts to life in Los Angeles. Meanwhile, Avery continues his campaign for city council.

title: Lethal Weapon: Need To Know
description: New partners Murtaugh and Cole attempt to find a steady rhythm as they work to solve the murder of a finance executive. Meanwhile, Cole navigates his role with his ex, Natalie, and his daughter, Maya, and Avery grapples with the outcome of his campaign for city council.

title: Lethal Weapon: A Whole Lotto Trouble
description: Cole juggles the realities of his job and his duty to be a good parent as he and Murtaugh work together to bust a gang running a lottery scam. Murtaugh prepares to celebrate his 30th year with the LAPD and receives a surprise visit from his competitive father-in-law.

title: Lethal Weapon: Leo Getz Justice
description: Cole reflects upon his time working for the CIA, as a person from the past makes a startling reappearance. Murtaugh struggles with his own mistakes after a murder raises questions about a suspect he put away years prior; and Leo Getz returns as the attorney on the case.

title: Lethal Weapon: Get The Picture
description: Murtaugh and Cole investigate after a robbery of a truck filled with fine art. Cole deals with lingering feelings for Natalie after a development in her life. Meanwhile, Riana blackmails Murtaugh into letting her go to a concert after she catches him in a lie.

title: Lethal Weapon: Panama
description: Cole confronts his past when his former mentor, Tom Barnes, delivers alarming news, as he and Murtaugh investigate a robbery of safe deposit boxes. Meanwhile, Murtaugh clashes with Trishs new client, Louie Gutierrez, and enlists Baileys help to investigate her.

title: Lethal Weapon: Bali
description: Murtaugh turns to Coles former mentor, Tom Barnes, for help on a high-stakes cartel case. Meanwhile, Murtaugh and Trish meet Natalie and Maya for the first time, and tensions mount between Bailey and "The Gute" as the new partners begin to work together.

title: Lethal Weapon: What The Puck
description: Cole wants to talk to Natalie about their relationship before its too late, but a wrench is thrown in his plans after he bumps into a new ADA, Erica. Meanwhile, after being kicked out of the house for Trishs girls night, Murtaugh finds himself an unlikely friend.

title: Lethal Weapon: Bad Santas
description: While Cole gets into the holiday spirit for his first Christmas with Maya, Murtaugh hopes he can convince RJ to come back home from Costa Rica for the holidays. At the precinct, Cole and Murtaugh are saddled with a complicated burglary and home invasion case.

title: Lethal Weapon: There Will Be Bud
description: Cole finds himself on the rebound, and his new romantic interest has an unexpected connection to the A.D.A., complicating things at work. Meanwhile, Murtaugh worries about the connection between a case hes working and an opportunity for Trish on a high-profile lawsuit.

title: Lethal Weapon: Dial M For Murtagh
description: Murtaugh takes a family vacation, but is pulled back into work when he witnesses an alleged abduction. Cole is left to investigate a murder himself, but the two cases begin to intersect.

title: Lethal Weapon: The Roger And Me
description: Murtaugh and Cole investigate the murder of an underground MMA fighter when Murtaugh realises his fighting moves arent as sharp as they once were. Meanwhile, Trish is unfulfilled by her practice and considers running for a public office.

title: Lethal Weapon: Coyote Ugly
description: When Cole and Murtaugh investigate a case involving a father and daughter crossing the Mexican border, they end up uncovering a major issue with California Boarder Patrol. Meanwhile, Trish prepares her campaign for D.A. and must face parts of her past.

title: Lethal Weapon: A Game Of Chicken
description: Against Murtaughs advice, Cole reaches out to Tom Barnes to help with a case that hits close to home, putting Murtaugh and Coles partnership to the test. Meanwhile, Trish prepares to announce her campaign for District Attorney.

title: Lethal Weapon: The Spy Who Loved Me

description: Nigella bakes a fluffy, white, no-knead bread, which she uses to sandwich her crispy fried chicken, accompanied by pickles and kimchi. She also takes the fear out of making fish stew and makes a daring cherry flambe.

description: Rick meets a man who is paid to eat 700 samples of cheese a week. He then heads to Newlyn, the unlikely setting of one of Britain’s most revolutionary art movements.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Caveman Lollipop
description: With her eyes set on winning the first prize of the first season, down-to-earth and affable Sara makes an unforgettable appearance as the first amateur chef and host to her competitors and hungry guests.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Balaleet
description: Handsome, confident Ali is the man of the hour, cooking up authentic Bahraini dishes and finding the time for intense workouts at the gym but will his good looks and charm be enough to win over his guests and get him the highest score for the evening?

title: Yalla Net`asha: Amazing Grace
description: Elegant, sophisticated and sharp as a knife, Grace is determined to win with her seafood recipes. Will it be enough or will she make a meal of it? No pun intended.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Hot stuff
description: Chef Halawa is in the house! Competition is heating up and things are too hot to handle, literally. It is all or nothing for Chef Halawa as he must win and win big to beat Grace’s high score, after all they don’t call him Chef for nothing!

title: Yalla Net`asha: Lady Gaga
description: In this episode, we meet Mohammed – a dentist by day and a fashion eccentric by night. But will his unusual choice of wardrobe and main course named after Lady Gaga, make his guests go gaga over his culinary skills or boo him behind his back?

title: Yalla Net`asha: Food for thought
description: An evening of spiritual healing is on the menu as Dr. Mariam seeks to impress her three guests with a selection of Zen food, tossed with meditation and an assortment of chanting. Looks like it will be food for thought for the skeptics and the believers alike!

title: Yalla Net`asha: Touch me if you can
description: It’s showtime for Tamer! The cinematographer swaps camera lenses for pots and pans and becomes the third host of this quartet. Unphased by previous dinners, his culinary skills are only surpassed by his mischiefs and he won’t stop until someone says “cut“.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Spice Girl
description: Hold on to your forks and knives as Mazoon is cooking seafood and coming out of her shell too. With her penchant for chilly, crazy antics in the kitchen and creative cooking, Spice Girl Mazoon might just upset the final score and win the 1000$ prize. Who knows?

title: Yalla Net`asha: Abdelrahman the Superman
description: Abdelrahman starts this round with a dose of pushups and special recipes to impress this eclectic mix of guests; but will his macho cooking style please everyone, or will Superman meet his kryptonite?

title: Yalla Net`asha: Saudi Delights
description: Saudi cuisine and hospitality take center stage as Zeina puts her tried and tested home-cooked recipes to the ultimate test. Contestants beware! She might look like a butterfly, but certainly stings like a bee.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Am cute and I know it!
description: She is into all things cute and fashionable but does Paola the popular influencer has what it takes to win the prize? It’s crunch time - but first, let’s take a selfie!

title: Yalla Net`asha: Edward Silverhands
description: Quietly observing the competition, Edward is the last one to cook, but will he be the first one to win. Surprise surprise - it’s a race to the finish line in this unpredictable group.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Bohemian night
description: Young, free and single, Jordanian Tuleen hopes her bohemian-themed night will be her recipe for success. Will it be a showstopper or a kitchen blooper?

title: Yalla Net`asha: Queen Sophie
description: She might be the one who put the Sophi in sophistication but her regal demeanor, acerbic comments and calory-laden dishes might just leave her guests with a bitter aftertaste.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Simba’s Pride
description: Stylish and handsome, heartthrob basketball champion Al Hassan wants the world to know that he’s got game in the kitchen too. But will this evening be a Slam dunk or Air Ball?

title: Yalla Net`asha: Tailspin Maya
description: Expect the unexpected in this episode as Maya is hosting a dinner party like no other! Starting from the front door where her guests are asked to remove one piece of clothing to enter. Uh Oh, Maya!

title: Yalla Net`asha: Aunty Souad
description: Souad, a Jordanian food expert will welcome Zeina, an Iraqi fashionista, Salma a blogger from Egypt, and Mohamad an amateur dancer from Saudi Arabia. The generation gap between them is at its peak, and some old grudges will leave 2 of the guests uncomfortable.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Shako Mako
description: Its time for the second dinner of the week! Zeina, the fashionista influencer enters the kitchen to prepare food for her guests. Fashion and cooking do not mix well for Zeina, who tries her best to impress her rivals with all possible tricks.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Lord of the Dance
description: YALLA NETASHAs third host of the week is Mohamad, the Saudi dancer who wants to top his 3 competitors. Mohamad however has one secret recipe which will amaze his guests. A twist of spices, some dance moves, and another generational clash. Turn the music on!

title: Yalla Net`asha: Salma Ya Salama
description: In this final dinner party, Salma the blogger from Egypt welcomes Souad, Zeina, and Mohamad for one final round. Unexpected ingredients are on the menu, and a never-before-seen character makes a surprise appearance.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Fired up Ragheed
description: A new week starts with Ragheed, a confident "chef" who dreamed of  hosting three women. Not only did his dream become reality; but the three ladies, an Egyptian picky eater, a Lebanese professional nagger, and an Emirati silent sniper might turn it into a nightmare

title: Yalla Net`asha: Picky Eater
description: In the second dinner of the week, Heba the picky eater prepares a seafood menu. How will this night unfold for her after not eating anything at the previous dinner and will the shaky alliance of three women against the alpha male last the night?

title: Yalla Net`asha: Bombshell Sahar
description: On the third night, Sahar our new host will try to overcome Ragheed by surprising everyone and revealing her true unique and non-traditional character. The surprise during the entertainment part however, is not a pleasant one especially for the traditional Ragheed.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Nags become gags
description: On the final night, Lamar the professional nagger’s turn has come to be under the scrutiny of her guests! With no room for nagging, she will encounter fundamental problems while cooking that force her to make many sacrifices.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Carnivore Mohsen
description: Mohsen, the multi-functional butcher from Lebanon welcomes 3 ladies: Rasha, Hanadi and Eman. Three against one in a battle of the sexes will keep Mohsen on the run to impress… if only he stops talking.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Masterchef  Rasha
description: The second host of the week on YALLA NETASHA is Levantine cuisine expert Rasha from Syria who made it clear that her expertise has no equal and she will surprise all her guests with food they could have never imagined eating or cooking.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Peach perfect Hanadi
description: The third night’s host is Hanadi, the beauty expert from Lebanon who laid low to give the impression of not being a worthy challenger. But under duress, it might be hard for her to focus, and she will have to rely on sisterhood to steer her ship to safety.

title: Yalla Net`asha: A touch of etiquette
description: The final dinner of the week is hosted by Eman, the etiquette expert from UAE . The four experts wait impatiently to see who can top the other and win but the night takes its downturn with an unexpected gesture from one of the guests.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Egyptino
description: Our first host is an Egyptian Filipino, who is proud of her mixed background, but she will face a real food detective. Adding to the mix is a Lebanese healer and a “no filter’ Syrian woman who will leave no table unturned.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Dima sikidim
description: Dima is tidying up the table for the best dining experience ever. While taking care of the finest details, Nooras phobias show up uninvited and bring turbulence to the whole situation and makes the dinner uneasy.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Noora La la Land!
description: Tonight’s the event that everyone has been waiting for! Finally, the guests will be introduced to Noora’s so-called ‘La la Land!’. After having a closer look into her dark world, will the contestants forgive her past or serve her some cold revenge?

title: Yalla Net`asha: Dalia  NRG
description: Tonight, Dalia has planned to heal her guests with relaxation therapy, but it turns into a recipe for disaster. Will she be able to finally bring about the calm or will the guests wish they were stuck in yesterday’s La la Land?

title: Yalla Net`asha: Couscous Happiness
description: The week begins with a Tunisian Happiness Coach, hosting a Lebanese health freak, a Jordanian foodie, who feels like a plate of hummus in a Japanese meal; and a shy Emirati pilot who probably wants to jump off a flying plane right now.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Captain Faisal
description: Captain Faisal is about to take his guests on a culinary flight, but will his cooking land smoothly on Remy’s health-conscious taste buds? That is not the only turbulence, Faisal has to deal with so fasten your seat belts.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Foodilicious Nariman
description: Tonight foodie Nariman decides to ignore her guest’s ‘specific tastes’, was it uber confidence or recklessness? Spoiler alert! She has got a secret recipe to ease last night’s tension between Remy and Salma. Will that be entertaining enough?

title: Yalla Net`asha: Sugar Free Remy
description: This is everyone’s chance at cold revenge as Remy puts on the chef’s hat. Watch out for Nariman’s sinister plans and Salma’s temper as she couldn’t even get past the appetizer before criticizing . Seems like, this food fight is about to get ugly

title: Yalla Net`asha: Bibi Rainbow
description: Happy Bashayer from Kuwait kicks off the season with a big splash of positivity and happiness. Miss congeniality will leave no pans unturned to woo her guests. A wishful thinking or uber confidence ? Lets find out!

title: Yalla Net`asha: Mr. Brainiac
description: He does not mince his words and he is here to win. Meet Abdelrahman, a self-confessed brainiac, a walking encyclopedia and Oud virtuoso but can he add excellence in cooking to his impressive CV?

title: Yalla Net`asha: Heidi of Egypt
description: With high hopes and Higher heels, Heidi wants to seal the deal and win the competition with her original recipes but with a minor handicap, she never tried them before.

title: Yalla Net`asha: From Chic to Chef
description: Fashion-conscious with eyes on the big prize, Sanad had one chance and one chance only to be more than a pretty face. In this group, nothing is certain and past alliances are as shaky as a vanilla milkshake.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Flower Power
description: Lama exudes confidence with her instagrammable smile and unique fashion style, but will it be enough to razzle dazzle her three hungry guests: Shifaa, Nazek and Musaed . The answer is definitely on the menu tonight .

title: Yalla Net`asha: Shifaa Jawjam
description: Shifaas honesty is not for everyones palette as she dishes out her acerbic comments with no sugarcoating. Tonight, she is on the kitchen frontline looking for swift victory or perhaps a truce. Time to bring up the ammunition and start cooking.

title: Yalla Net`asha: N For Nazek
description: Nazek set the bar high for her in previous episodes with her poignant observations. let’s hope her dinner party is not overshadowed by bitter simmering rivalries between two ladies at opposite ends of the spectrum of friendship. let the fun begin.

title: Yalla Net`asha: The Trailblazer
description: It is the last dinner and travel blogger Musaed takes us on a world tour of culinary delights. But there is a storm brewing as typhoon Shifaa and Lama reach category five. Fasten your seat belts, it is going to be a bumpy ride as we discover who will land the 1000$.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Afrobeats
description: Hip-hop meets chop-chop, Khorri is dishing out Afrobeats, smart moves and his signature tasty stake to his unsuspecting guests. Will his youthful enthusiasm and affable personality melts everyone’s iceberg tonight? Drumroll !

title: Yalla Net`asha: Let’s get down to business
description: Enthused with patriotism and culinary passion, business savvy Eman takes center stage in tonights competition as she aims to woo her guests with authentic Emirati cuisine, will they dig in or opt out ?

title: Yalla Net`asha: Nesrine Supermom
description: Mumsy and kind, Nisrine is all about nurturing and providing wholesome meals for her newly adopted family. But this Mother Goose soon becomes Mother of Dragons when she enters the kitchen , just don’t criticize her home cooking.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Bad boy Moey
description: The day of reckoning is nigh for Moey. After tormenting everyone with his sharp critique of etiquettes or lack of, it is his turn to host the dinner party and there are no friendly faces to be seen at the table. It is the night of the long knives!

title: Yalla Net`asha: Al Fresco Dining with Badr
